== 概論 ==
兩國於1954年建交關係，而印度於1957年在[[華沙|華沙]]開設了[[印度駐波蘭大使館|印度駐波蘭大使館]]。在[[冷戰|冷戰]]期間，印度和波蘭與[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的關係均十分密切，兩國亦因此邦交緊密。1977年1月25日，兩國之間就航空服務在新德里簽訂協議<ref>{{cite journal|title=Indo-Polish Agreement on Air Services|journal=Foreign Affairs Record|date=January 1977|volume=XXIII|issue=1|page=2|url=http://mealib.nic.in/far/1977.pdf|accessdate=6 August 2013|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020040105/http://mealib.nic.in/far/1977.pdf|archive-date=2013-10-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[蘇聯解體|蘇聯解體]]後，兩國都致力改善與[[歐盟|歐盟]]和[[美國|美國]]的關係，而兩國關係至今亦保持友好。波蘭在1989年共產主義制度被推翻後，印度和波蘭議會建立交往。2009年4月，[[印度總統|印度總統]][[普拉蒂巴·帕蒂爾|普拉蒂巴·帕蒂爾]]訪問波蘭<ref name="Indo-Polish relations">{{cite web |url=http://www.indianembassy.pl/iprelation.html |title=Indo-Polish relations |publisher=Embassy of India in Poland. |accessdate=2009-09-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20031031155652/http://www.indianembassy.pl/iprelation.html |archivedate=2003-10-31 }}</ref>；2010年9月，[[波蘭總理|波蘭總理]][[圖斯克|圖斯克]]訪問印度，會見了印度政客和商人。

== 經貿關係 ==
2008年，兩國之間的雙邊貿易總額比1992年增長約11倍<ref name="Indo-Polish relations" />。於2005年期間，印度一些企業簽訂投資協議，相關投資創造可在波蘭預期創造3500個新職位<ref name=" India, Poland to boost economic ties ">{{cite news|url=http://in.ibtimes.com/articles/20060518/poland-kamal-nath-commerce-economic-trade-investment.htm|title=India, Poland to boost economic ties|first=Surojit Chatterjee|date=18 May 2006|publisher=IBTimes India|accessdate=2008-11-04|archive-date=2006-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061024124453/http://in.ibtimes.com/articles/20060518/poland-kamal-nath-commerce-economic-trade-investment.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。印度主要出口到波蘭的產品包括[[茶|茶]]、[[咖啡|咖啡]]、[[香料|香料]]、[[紡織品|紡織品]]、[[藥品|藥品]]、[[機械器材|機械器材]]、[[醫療器材|醫療器材]]及[[汽車零件|汽車零件]]等，波蘭出口到印度的商品則包括機械和[[電子設備|電子設備]]、[[人造樹脂|人造樹脂]]、[[塑料|塑料]]、[[有色金屬|有色金屬]]及[[機床|機床]]<ref name="POLISH ECONOMY-Foreign Trade">{{cite web|url=http://cii.in/menu_content.php?menu_id=1127|title=POLISH ECONOMY-Foreign Trade|publisher=Confedaration of Indian Industry|accessdate=2008-11-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20110719000435/http://cii.in/menu_content.php?menu_id=1127|archivedate=2011-07-19}}</ref>。{{link-en|印度工業聯合會|Confederation of Indian Industry}}曾多次組團到波蘭，探討在各個經濟領域的合作機會<ref name="Polish companies seek closer ties with India">{{cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/Economy/Polish_cos_seek_closer_ties_with_India/articleshow/3072628.cms|title=Polish companies seek closer ties with India|date=26 May 2008|work=IANS|publisher=Economic Times|accessdate=2008-11-04|archive-date=2008-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630094740/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/Economy/Polish_cos_seek_closer_ties_with_India/articleshow/3072628.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些印度企業在波蘭成立分部<ref name="POLISH ECONOMY-Foreign Trade">{{cite web|url=http://cii.in/menu_content.php?menu_id=1127|title=POLISH ECONOMY-Foreign Trade|publisher=Confedaration of Indian Industry|accessdate=2008-11-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20110719000435/http://cii.in/menu_content.php?menu_id=1127|archivedate=2011-07-19}}</ref>。成立於2008年的[[印度－波蘭商會和工會|印度－波蘭商會和工會]]負責保護雙方的經濟利益，並促進印度和波蘭之間的經濟關係<ref name="POLISH ECONOMY-Foreign Trade" />。波蘭曾表示有興趣建立兩國之間的直飛航班<ref name="Poland invites Indian investments with focus on SME sector ">{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2008/01/15/stories/2008011552261000.htm|title=Poland invites Indian investments with focus on SME sector|date=Jan 15, 2008|publisher=Business Daily from THE HINDU|accessdate=2008-11-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090131055513/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2008/01/15/stories/2008011552261000.htm|archivedate=2009-01-31|df=}}</ref>。

== 軍事關係 ==
印度與波蘭近年開始發展軍事上的合作，例如協助培訓參與[[聯合國維和行動|聯合國維和行動]]的[[軍人|軍人]]及在[[軍演|軍演]]中交換觀察員<ref name="Indian Army chief to visit Poland, Belarus ">{{cite web|url=http://www.nerve.in/news:253500133794|title=Indian Army chief to visit Poland, Belarus|date=7 March 2008|publisher=NERVE|accessdate=2008-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719063859/http://www.nerve.in/news:253500133794|archive-date=2011-07-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。兩國在2003年2月簽署了防務合作[[諒解備忘錄|諒解備忘錄]]；印度也曾簽署價值6億[[美元|美元]]的合同，協助波蘭開發現代化的軍備，兩國更曾考慮互相投資對方的[[國防工業|國防工業]]<ref name="India, Poland deepen defence ties ">{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2004/03/20/stories/2004032004031400.htm|title=India, Poland deepen defence ties|first=C. Raja Mohan|date=Mar 20, 2004|publisher=The Hindu|accessdate=2008-10-11|archive-date=2004-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040413033915/http://www.hindu.com/2004/03/20/stories/2004032004031400.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

